  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Goal is to examine the efficy of Cardiac Resynchronization Therapy in heart failure patients
      with narrow QRS complex and optimized medical treatment but echocardiographic
      desynchronization detection as well as the positve increase of the intraoperative
      pressureincreasespeed in reverse remodelling and a secondary improvement of functional
      parameters
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
